<h2>Silent Auction</h2>

<p>Despite COVID-19 Team DG are still trying to fundraise and help make Dunton Green Primary School an even better place to learn.</p>

{% if status.live == 'true' %}

<p>Browse the items below and fill in the form on the item pages to make a bid. Highest bid wins - a great chance to grab some bargains (<a href="/rules/">read full rules here</a>).</p>

<ul class="item_list">
  {%- for lot in auctionLots -%}
    <li class="item_list__item item">
      <div class="item__image-container">
        <p class="item__value">Worth Â£{{ lot.total_value }}</p>
        <img class="item__image" src="{{lot.image}}" alt="" />
      </div>
      <h3 class="item__title" ><span class="item__number">{{ loop.index }}.</span> {{ lot.lot }}</h3>

      {% for item in lot.items %}
        {% if loop.length == 1 and loop.last == true %}
          <p class="item_list__count">{{ loop.length }} item:</p>
        {% elif loop.last == true %}
          <p class="item_list__count">{{ loop.length }} items:</p>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
      <ul>
        {% for item in lot.items %}
            <li>{{ item.short_name }}</li>
        {%- endfor -%}
      </ul>

      <a href="lots/{{ lot.lot | slug }}" class="btn">See more and bid</a>
    </li>
  {%- endfor -%}
</ul>

